    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo Nahwē tu ne tohpi\npeeminnehts/ kas flawehs tewi\nKappa?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es esinu peekuffs no man-\nnas Waideschānas/ es darru fa-\nwu Gultu zaurn Nakti peldam/\nes flazzinaju ar mannahn Asta-\nrahm nannu Gultu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Manna Azz irr noginduti\nno Skummibas/ un irr nowez,\nzejsi mannu Waidneeku deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atkahpeet no mannim wit-\nfi Taunadarrtaji/ jo tas KUNGS\nklaufa mannu Randaschanas\nBalsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS klaufa\nmannu Luhgsehanu/ mannu Pee-\nluhgsehanu tas KUNGS pee-\nnem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſteem manneem Ee-\nnaidnekeem buhs Kauna tapt/\nfohti iſtruhzinatees/ atpakat\ngreestees/ un Kauna tapt pee-\npeſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta VII. Dseefma.\nWeena luhdsama Dseefma par Jsglahbschanu\nno teem Wajatajeem : 2. Jo wiſch finnahs\nnenoseedsigu jew eſam : 4. Un Deews wehl\nehu weens taiſns Sohgis : 12. Kas teem\nBesdeewigem gann kahdu Brihdi Wattu\nleek : 13. Bet pehzgalla jo gruhtaki johda :\n14.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ahwida * daschadiga\nOseefma/ ko wiſch tam\nKUNGAM dseedaja /\npar Kuſa Jemini Dehla Lee-\ntahm.\n* Tas irr, kas us daschadu Wihsi dseedama.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS mans Deews/\nus tevi es paluischohs/ atpesti\nmanni no wiſteem manneem Wa-\njatajeem/ un isglahb manni/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tas mannu Dweh\nne laupa ka Lauwa to faplo-\ndams/ tadeht ka Jsglahbeja\nwaid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS mans Deew\nesinut es fcho darrijs/ ja Neta-\nniba irr mannas Rohkās.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Esinu es Lauwu maſta-\ntam/ kas meerigi ar manni\ndshwoja/ ka es ne buhtu isgla-\nbis to/ kas manni bes Wain-\napbehdinaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad lai tas Eenaidnee-\nmannu Dwehfeli waja/ un wi-\nxu panahk/ un faininn manni\nDshwibu pee Semmes/ un no-\nleek mannu Godhibu Pihfschlō-\nSela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zellees af KUNGS! eekſe-\ntawas Dutmibas/ usmohstee-\npahr to Bahrsibu manna Pret-\ntineeka/ ir mannis labbad us-\nmohstees/ tahs Teefas deht/ fe-\ntu eſti pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka to Lauschu Draudse ap-\nkahrt teivi mettahs/ un to paſchu-\ndeht iszellees attak angſit.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS nefibe-\nteem Laudini to Teetu/ teefa-\nmanni af KUNGS! pehz man-\nnas Taifnibas un Beswaini-\nbas/ kas pee mannim irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lai jelle to Besdeewigō\nNiknumam Gals tohp/ bet ap-\nstiprini to Taifnibu/ kas tu Sir-\ndis un Ihktis pahrmannt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mannas preekſchturra-\nmas Brunnas irr pee Deewa/\nkas rahnahm Sirdim palihds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Deews irr weens taiſns\nSoh-\n"
    }
  ],
